Low Risk                ████████████████████ 6
________________________________________
🔧 Recommended Security Headers to Implement
http
Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
Set-Cookie: sessionId=xyz; SameSite=Lax; Secure; HttpOnly
________________________________________
📌 Conclusion
OWASP Juice Shop contains 8 distinct security vulnerabilities, categorized as:
•	🟠 2 Medium Risk vulnerabilities (Unsanitized reviews, No rate limiting)
•	🟡 6 Low Risk vulnerabilities (Missing headers, Info disclosure)
Key Takeaways:
Issue	Status
❌ Unsanitized user reviews allowing stored XSS	Needs Immediate Fix
❌ No rate limiting enabling abuse of review system	Needs Immediate Fix
❌ Missing security headers across all responses	Needs Implementation
Immediate remediation should focus on input sanitization and rate limiting, followed by security header implementation in the next development sprint.
